[{"question":"How did she get to the top of the business world?","answer":"I wanted to be a business person.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":7,"aSentId":8},{"question":"You know how would you sum up marriage to the Hulk?","answer":"You know, well, we were married for 24 years, and you know, it was great.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":25,"aSentId":26},{"question":"Do you feel that the relationship basically floundered the moment you heard he\u0027d been unfaithful to you?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":42,"aSentId":43},{"question":"Why did he tell you?","answer":"Well, in my opinion I think the reason that he had to tell me was because the woman that he was philandering with had filed a lawsuit against him, and it was probably about to be public, and I think that if he had me on his side, that they could roll it out as extortion like a lot of these celebrities do.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":53,"aSentId":54},{"question":"If you\u0027re honest when you\u0027d seen other famous people get caught up in a scandal like that, and the woman stayed with the man, what was your view of women that did that before it happened to you?","answer":"Before, you know, I hadn\u0027t been in that position, so I just figured that publicly they were staying with their man because of usually politicians is what you heard.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":60,"aSentId":61},{"question":"Have you\u0027d gone through that thought in your head and thought, I would leave him?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":64,"aSentId":65},{"question":"How many other women do you think there probably were?","answer":"You know, just a rough guess I think there might have been three or four, but, you know, that\u0027s just my guess.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":74,"aSentId":75},{"question":"Did you have days when you wish you were still with him?","answer":"Oh, yes.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":88,"aSentId":89},{"question":"Does he regret it, do you think?","answer":"I think he does.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":99,"aSentId":100},{"question":"Has he tried to win you back?","answer":"You know, because we were going through so much stuff with the divorce and then, of course, my son had that tragic accident, and there was just a lot on our plate to sort out, and I think that he had already moved on to a new girlfriend by the time I had filed for divorce.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":102,"aSentId":103},{"question":"And is it 10 times worse when it has to be conducted in the public eye because you\u0027re with a famous guy?","answer":"It is.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":126,"aSentId":127},{"question":"There aren\u0027t many of him to the (INAUDIBLE), are there?","answer":"It was phenomenal being married to him.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":139,"aSentId":140},{"question":"Do you blame Terry for the fact that he took the car out?","answer":"You know, I\u0027m sure Terry trusted Nick, but he should have maybe thought a little bit more about the conditions, the fact that the boys were jet skiing all day and they were out in the hot sun.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":190,"aSentId":191},{"question":"How did you deal with that?","answer":"It was actually shocking.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":205,"aSentId":206},{"question":"Do you know?","answer":"John, I believe, is now out of the hospital and he\u0027s home.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":214,"aSentId":215},{"question":"Do you have any contact with his family?","answer":"I don\u0027t.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":218,"aSentId":219},{"question":"How did that make you feel?","answer":"Well, that was a blow.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":279,"aSentId":280},{"question":"She talks all about how she\u0027s sorry and that this love affair they had couldn\u0027t be denied, blah, blah, blah, and I was like, are you kidding me?","answer":"That was like a final kick in the teeth for you.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":306,"aSentId":307},{"question":"You know, living with the enemy, you know?","answer":"Yes, yes.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":323,"aSentId":324},{"question":"I bet part of you was thinking exactly that, checkmate, right?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":336,"aSentId":337},{"question":"I mean he\u0027s like a young Hulk, isn\u0027t he?","answer":"Yeah, he is.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":340,"aSentId":341},{"question":"How does Terry deal with Charlie?","answer":"He doesn\u0027t really like the idea.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":356,"aSentId":357},{"question":"When you know what you want to do, do something?","answer":"Well, it\u0027s go for yours.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":505,"aSentId":506},{"question":"Pretty embarrassing, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"I don\u0027t think so because --","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":645,"aSentId":646},{"question":"Do you ever have that feeling?","answer":"I just love how much my husband loves my daughter.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":703,"aSentId":704},{"question":"Once you\u0027re a businesswoman and you\u0027ve got the cover of \"Forbes Magazine,\" then what do you do?","answer":"You give back.","docId":"110628pmt","qSentId":713,"aSentId":714}]